ults that occur within itself and to adapt to its\nsurroundings without human intervention.	t	t	t	0	0	0	Biomimicry is one of the most inspiring fields around which present day robotics researches revolve. It is our technology exchange with mother nature, who cranks out newer and newer designs that we have never even dreamt of and many that we havent been able to figure out yet. The reason...		f		f		zinnia/_entry_detail.html	entry_detail.html			37
